Class HMSPersonnel

java.lang.Object
model.HMSPersonnel
Direct Known Subclasses:
Admin, Doctor, Patient, Pharmacist
public class HMSPersonnel extends Object
Represents a personnel in the Hospital Management System (HMS). This class holds personal and contact details for a personnel, as well as their role in the system. Implements Serializable to allow object serialization.

      public HMSPersonnel(String UID, String fullName, String idCard, String username, String email, String phoneNo, String passwordHash, LocalDateTime DoB, String gender, String role)
      Constructs a new HMSPersonnel object with the specified details.
      Parameters:
      UID - the unique ID for the personnel
      fullName - the full name of the personnel
      idCard - the identification card number of the personnel
      username - the username of the personnel for system login
      email - the email address of the personnel
      phoneNo - the phone number of the personnel
      passwordHash - the hashed password for the personnel's account
      DoB - the date of birth of the personnel
      gender - the gender of the personnel
      role - the role or position of the personnel in the system
